snippet.title: [Gamesiety] The Bunny Hill Horror Playthrough
snippet.description:
By popular demand (well, a lot of people on Newgrounds were complaining about the game's difficulty), here are Pennsylvania's finest streamer team, Gamesiety, with their playthrough of The Bunny Hill Horror by Krunchy Fried Games. You'll laugh, you'll cry, you'll wonder if they'll ever solve that puzzle with the old paintings. Enjoy... 

Gamesiety on Twitch:  https://www.twitch.tv/gamesiety
The Bunny Hill Horror on itch.io: https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io/bunny-hill-horror
Krunchy Fried Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/KFriedGames

The concluding chapter is playable here: https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io/bunny-hill-horror-bunny-boiler
